  "original_title": "\u0db8\u0dc4\u0db1\u0dd4\u0dc0\u0dbb \u0d9a\u0ddd\u0da7\u0dd2\u0db4\u0dad\u0dd2 \u0d9a\u0dad\u0d9c\u0dda \u0d9d\u0dcf\u0dad\u0d9a\u0dba\u0dcf \u0d85\u0dbd\u0dca\u0dbd\u0dba\u0dd2",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "The killer of Kandy millionaire Kata is caught",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "The police say that the woman's close relative and a person have been arrested on suspicion of the case of the death of a 64-year-old woman who was living alone in a large house near the Ratu Bokkuva Junction in Lake Waya Raum, Kandy.",
        "The police say that the two suspects who were arrested on suspicion are residents of Kadawata and Delgoda, aged 52 and 62. The police also say that the knife used to kill the woman was found thrown in the forest behind the house of the main suspect in Delgoda.",
        "This woman was brutally murdered by cutting her throat at around 2 pm on the 14th in her home and while the police investigation was going on through several departments, Chief Inspector M. G. S. According to information received by Mr. Bandara, the related suspects have been arrested in Delgoda and Kadawata areas.",
        "The arrested suspects were supposed to be brought to Kandy and during the questioning of the suspects, the main suspect told the police that the woman was killed due to hatred due to the fact that the property of the murdered woman was not properly divided among her children. The police say that he himself has come to kill the woman."
      ],
